Dialogue: 100,0:00:53.28,0:00:54.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Așa...
Dialogue: 100,0:00:56.28,0:00:59.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Asigură-te că asculți de unchiul tău.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:59.19,0:01:00.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bine.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:00.36,0:01:02.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ți-ai luat batista? Dar biletul?
Dialogue: 100,0:01:02.24,0:01:04.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,O pereche drăguță de încălțări?
Dialogue: 100,0:01:04.36,0:01:05.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stai, asta e tot ce iei la tine?
Dialogue: 100,0:01:05.78,0:01:08.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Este în regulă. \NLe-am luat pe cele negre.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:08.95,0:01:11.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Asigură-te că nu-ți uiți \Nbagajul în tren, bine?
Dialogue: 100,0:01:11.67,0:01:13.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Și nu uita să cobori la stația corectă.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:13.80,0:01:15.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Da, am înțeles!
Dialogue: 100,0:01:15.68,0:01:19.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Doamne. Am fost acolo în \Nfiecare an, deci voi fi în regulă.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:19.15,0:01:22.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hei, pune-ți o pălărie pe cap. \NVei face insolație.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:22.63,0:01:25.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Este în regulă! Voi fi bine.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:27.56,0:01:28.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Am plecat!
Dialogue: 100,0:01:57.13,0:01:59.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Prima oară l-am întâlnit
Dialogue: 100,0:02:01.47,0:02:03.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}când aveam șase ani.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:14.01,0:02:15.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Într-o zi toridă de vară,
Dialogue: 100,0:02:15.95,0:02:19.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}m-am pierdut în pădurea zeului muntelui,
Dialogue: 100,0:02:19.82,0:02:21.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}care se zvonea a fi locul unde trăiesc spiritele.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:24.86,0:02:27.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}După ce am alergat împrejur căutând o ieșire,
Dialogue: 100,0:02:27.55,0:02:29.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}am obosit atât de tare încât \Nabia mă mai puteam mișca.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:30.56,0:02:35.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Când am început să plâng deoarece eram singură și speriată,
Dialogue: 100,0:02:35.98,0:02:38.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}el a părut înaintea mea.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:41.25,0:02:42.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hei! Micuțo!
Dialogue: 100,0:03:02.55,0:03:04.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,De ce plângi?
Dialogue: 100,0:03:08.27,0:03:11.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,O persoană! Sunt salvată!
Dialogue: 100,0:03:24.71,0:03:26.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,S-Scuze.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:28.15,0:03:31.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ești un copil uman, nu-i așa?
Dialogue: 100,0:03:32.58,0:03:35.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dacă sunt atins de un om, voi dispărea.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:38.18,0:03:40.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dacă ești atins de un om?
Dialogue: 100,0:03:41.07,0:03:43.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tu nu ești un om?
Dialogue: 100,0:03:44.41,0:03:47.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eu... sunt ceva care trăiește în această pădure.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:48.89,0:03:51.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ce? Atunci... ești unul dintre spirite?
Dialogue: 100,0:03:52.74,0:03:56.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dar... ce vrei să spui prin faptul că vei dispărea?
Dialogue: 100,0:04:21.13,0:04:24.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,C-Chiar nu ești om...
Dialogue: 100,0:04:27.07,0:04:31.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Niciun om nu ar lovi un copil astfel!
Dialogue: 100,0:04:32.97,0:04:37.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A dispărea înseamnă a nu mai exista.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:38.78,0:04:42.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aceasta este vraja pe care a pus-o zeul muntelui asupra mea.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:44.50,0:04:46.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dacă voi fi atins de un om,
Dialogue: 100,0:04:47.95,0:04:49.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,acela va fi sfârșitul meu.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:52.00,0:04:55.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Î-Îmi pare rău.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:55.05,0:04:56.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Poftim, micuțo.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:57.73,0:04:59.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Prinde-te de celălalt capăt.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:00.23,0:05:01.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Te-ai pierdut, nu-i așa?
Dialogue: 100,0:05:02.76,0:05:04.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Te voi ajuta să ieși din pădure.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:06.70,0:05:08.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mulțumesc!
Dialogue: 100,0:05:12.97,0:05:14.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nu ți-am spus mai devreme?
Dialogue: 100,0:05:14.03,0:05:17.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Scuze, nu m-am putut abține...
Dialogue: 100,0:05:32.00,0:05:34.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Parcă am fi la o întâlnire!
Dialogue: 100,0:05:35.02,0:05:36.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nu una foarte romantică...
Dialogue: 100,0:05:44.10,0:05:46.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hei... nu îți este teamă.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:48.83,0:05:49.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,De ce anume?
Dialogue: 100,0:05:50.91,0:05:51.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nu mai contează.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:55.67,0:05:58.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dacă vei merge drept înainte, vei ajunge la poteca muntelui.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:59.71,0:06:00.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Pa.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:01.98,0:06:04.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Vei fi mereu aici?
Dialogue: 100,0:06:05.09,0:06:07.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dacă mă voi întoarce, \Nne vom revedea?
Dialogue: 100,0:06:08.19,0:06:10.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Asta este pădurea unde \Ntrăiesc spiritele și zeul muntelui.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:12.38,0:06:14.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Intră în ea și te vei pierde pe vecie.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:16.69,0:06:17.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nu ar trebui să vii aici.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:18.98,0:06:21.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Asta e ceea ce spun sătenii, nu-i așa?
Dialogue: 100,0:06:25.65,0:06:27.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Numele meu este Takegawa Hotaru.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:28.41,0:06:29.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Al tău?
Dialogue: 100,0:06:49.03,0:06:52.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oricum, mă voi întoarce mâine cu un cadou de mulțumire!
Dialogue: 100,0:06:52.70,0:06:53.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Pa!
Dialogue: 100,0:06:54.04,0:06:54.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Gin.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:13.73,0:07:14.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hotaru!
Dialogue: 100,0:07:14.53,0:07:16.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, unchiule!
Dialogue: 100,0:07:17.59,0:07:21.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hotaru, proasto!
Dialogue: 100,0:07:21.54,0:07:24.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ce ai fi făcut dacă te răneai prin pădure?
Dialogue: 100,0:07:37.72,0:07:38.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Unchiule.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:38.64,0:07:39.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ce este?
Dialogue: 100,0:07:40.31,0:07:43.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Este adevărat că trăiesc \Nspirite în acea pădure?
Dialogue: 100,0:07:43.71,0:07:46.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,O, pădurea zeului muntelui... Cine știe.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:46.95,0:07:48.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Așa se zvonește.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:53.94,0:07:58.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Când eram copil, voiam să văd spiritele, \Ndeci eu și prietenii mei mergeam adesea în pădure.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:59.35,0:08:05.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,În cele din urmă, nu am văzut vreodată unul, dar aveam \Nsenzația că uneori zăream ceva cu coada ochiului.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:06.74,0:08:11.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,În nopțile de vară, puteai auzi sunetul râului venind din pădure.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:11.41,0:08:18.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Și acum că stau să mă gândesc, Iwa a spus că ea și prietenii ei s-au distrat la un festival de vară în pădure.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:18.66,0:08:22.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dar sătenii nu ar fi ținut \Nniciodată un festival în pădure.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:23.27,0:08:25.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Atunci, al cui festival să fi fost?
Dialogue: 100,0:08:26.70,0:08:32.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Apoi a dat naștere acestei povești nebunești cum că trebuie să se strecoare la un festival al spiritelor.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:35.22,0:08:38.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Vai, ce de amintiri!
Dialogue: 100,0:08:38.22,0:08:41.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eram așa de proști când eram copii.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:12.27,0:09:15.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Asta este pădurea unde \Ntrăiesc spiritele și zeul muntelui.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:16.43,0:09:18.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Intră în ea și te vei pierde pe vecie.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:42.68,0:09:43.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ai venit.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:46.11,0:09:48.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nu credeam că te vei întoarce.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:49.49,0:09:50.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,M-ai...
Dialogue: 100,0:09:52.51,0:09:54.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,M-ai așteptat!
Dialogue: 100,0:09:59.33,0:10:01.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nu te înveți minte niciodată, nu?
Dialogue: 100,0:10:02.18,0:10:04.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Am fost așa fericită încât \Nnu m-am putut abține...
Dialogue: 100,0:10:04.21,0:10:05.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Scuze.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:07.72,0:10:08.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Este un pic cam cald aici.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:09.63,0:10:11.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Vrei să mergem undeva mai răcoros?
Dialogue: 100,0:10:11.45,0:10:12.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ce?
Dialogue: 100,0:10:12.99,0:10:14.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nu-ți face griji.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:14.64,0:10:16.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Te voi ajuta din nou să ieși.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:11.67,0:11:12.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Gin.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:13.37,0:11:16.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Acela este un copil uman?
Dialogue: 100,0:11:18.20,0:11:20.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Pot să-l mănânc?
Dialogue: 100,0:11:22.12,0:11:22.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nu.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:23.87,0:11:24.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Este prietenul meu.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:25.23,0:11:26.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Serios?
Dialogue: 100,0:11:27.24,0:11:28.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Copil uman.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:29.15,0:11:32.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Te rog să nu-i atingi pielea lui Gin.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:33.10,0:11:38.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dacă o vei face, te voi mânca!
Dialogue: 100,0:11:43.65,0:11:45.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh! O vulpe?
Dialogue: 100,0:11:49.40,0:11:50.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Este un spirit.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:52.08,0:11:55.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Se transformă ca să sperie oamenii, \Ndar este numai gura de el.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:59.21,0:12:01.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uimitor!
Dialogue: 100,0:12:01.00,0:12:04.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Asta este prima oară când \Nam văzut un spirit adevărat!
Dialogue: 100,0:12:04.03,0:12:05.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Deci chiar există!
Dialogue: 100,0:12:05.46,0:12:09.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uimitor! Incredibil! Fantastic!
Dialogue: 100,0:12:05.46,0:12:09.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Deci ce credeai că eram?
Dialogue: 100,0:12:13.56,0:12:15.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Gin, nu ai față sau ceva asemănător?
Dialogue: 100,0:12:16.31,0:12:18.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,De ce porți mască? {COVID.}
Dialogue: 100,0:12:18.28,0:12:19.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fără vreun motiv anume. {Still COVID.}
Dialogue: 100,0:12:21.74,0:12:22.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dar nu contează asta.
Dialogue: 100,0:12:23.35,0:12:24.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Spune-mi mai multe despre tine.
Dialogue: 100,0:12:26.83,0:12:27.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ești curios?
Dialogue: 100,0:12:29.40,0:12:30.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,De asta te-am așteptat.
Dialogue: 100,0:12:38.69,0:12:43.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}În ziua următoare și în zilele de după, am tot mers în pădure.
Dialogue: 100,0:12:45.53,0:12:50.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}În acele zile de vară, alergam și mă jucam peste tot pe munte.
Dialogue: 100,0:12:53.87,0:12:55.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aici, aici!
Dialogue: 100,0:12:56.65,0:12:58.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Este mai bine acolo.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:01.42,0:13:02.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Gata.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:03.49,0:13:04.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mersi!
Dialogue: 100,0:13:13.74,0:13:15.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Chiar dacă era copilăresc,
Dialogue: 100,0:13:16.30,0:13:18.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}mă distram foarte tare.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:42.11,0:13:45.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oare a adormit Gin?
Dialogue: 100,0:13:53.06,0:13:56.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Este în regulă dacă-i ating masca, nu-i așa?
Dialogue: 100,0:14:13.32,0:14:15.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, scuze!
Dialogue: 100,0:14:15.60,0:14:17.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Auci!
Dialogue: 100,0:14:18.01,0:14:22.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Să ataci pe cineva care doarme... \NChiar ești o domnișoară înfiorătoare.
Dialogue: 100,0:14:22.12,0:14:24.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Îmi cer scuze, dar...
Dialogue: 100,0:14:25.19,0:14:27.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,te prefăceai că dormi, nu-i așa?
Dialogue: 100,0:14:29.79,0:14:31.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Arăt normal, nu-i așa?
Dialogue: 100,0:14:33.71,0:14:35.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,De ce porți acea mască?
Dialogue: 100,0:14:36.57,0:14:38.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dacă nu o port,
Dialogue: 100,0:14:39.08,0:14:40.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,nu arăt ca un spirit, nu?
Dialogue: 100,0:14:52.63,0:14:53.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ești ciudat.
Dialogue: 100,0:15:02.29,0:15:03.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hei, Gin.
Dialogue: 100,0:15:05.12,0:15:07.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nu voi mai putea
Dialogue: 100,0:15:08.06,0:15:09.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,să vin aici mâine.
Dialogue: 100,0:15:11.06,0:15:12.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ți-am mai spus, nu-i așa?
Dialogue: 100,0:15:13.32,0:15:16.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Că stau la unchiul meu \Ndoar pe timpul verii, nu?
Dialogue: 100,0:15:17.17,0:15:20.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Deci va trebui să mă întorc acasă de mâine.
Dialogue: 100,0:15:27.00,0:15:28.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Vei putea veni din nou anul viitor?
Dialogue: 100,0:15:32.61,0:15:33.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Da!
Dialogue: 100,0:15:36.92,0:15:38.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Așa a devenit vara
Dialogue: 100,0:15:39.62,0:15:42.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}un lucru pe care-l așteptam.
Dialogue: 100,0:15:52.98,0:15:57.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Gin a așteptat să ne revedem vara următoare.
Dialogue: 100,0:15:59.05,0:16:00.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,E așa de rece!
Dialogue: 100,0:16:02.71,0:16:04.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ești așa ciudată!
Dialogue: 100,0:16:04.62,0:16:06.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Evident că apa e rece.
Dialogue: 100,0:16:19.27,0:16:19.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Gin!
Dialogue: 100,0:16:21.48,0:16:22.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Gin!
Dialogue: 100,0:16:22.96,0:16:24.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ai grijă, Gin.
Dialogue: 100,0:16:24.81,0:16:27.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Acela este un copil uman.
Dialogue: 100,0:16:27.09,0:16:30.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dacă te atinge, vei dispărea.
Dialogue: 100,0:16:30.96,0:16:31.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mersi.
Dialogue: 100,0:16:33.13,0:16:34.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sunt bine.
Dialogue: 100,0:16:41.45,0:16:45.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Te rog să nu-l atingi, copil uman.
Dialogue: 100,0:16:46.73,0:16:47.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Da.
Dialogue: 100,0:16:56.78,0:16:57.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Gin.
Dialogue: 100,0:16:59.07,0:17:00.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ai grijă.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:04.09,0:17:08.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Spiritele îl pot atinge, nu-i așa?
Dialogue: 100,0:17:10.23,0:17:13.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Au trecut două veri. Apoi trei.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:15.15,0:17:16.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hotaru!
Dialogue: 100,0:17:18.66,0:17:19.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Unde ești?
Dialogue: 100,0:17:22.34,0:17:23.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hotaru.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:24.05,0:17:24.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hota—
Dialogue: 100,0:17:28.68,0:17:30.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ce tot faci?
Dialogue: 100,0:17:33.10,0:17:36.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Voiam să-ți văd fața speriată, dar...
Dialogue: 100,0:17:42.70,0:17:44.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Măcar atunci când suntem doar noi doi,
Dialogue: 100,0:17:44.74,0:17:47.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,îți poți da masca jos din când în când?
Dialogue: 100,0:17:48.37,0:17:49.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bine,
Dialogue: 100,0:17:49.87,0:17:51.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,dar de ce?
Dialogue: 100,0:17:52.05,0:17:54.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nu am un motiv anume, dar—
Dialogue: 100,0:17:56.79,0:17:57.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ai grijă, Hota—
Dialogue: 100,0:18:10.03,0:18:11.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A fost pe-aproape.
Dialogue: 100,0:18:14.02,0:18:15.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Da...
Dialogue: 100,0:18:17.59,0:18:18.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Îmi pare rău, Hotaru.
Dialogue: 100,0:18:19.79,0:18:20.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ești bine?
Dialogue: 100,0:18:25.44,0:18:26.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ce ușurare.
Dialogue: 100,0:18:28.73,0:18:29.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hei, Gin.
Dialogue: 100,0:18:34.10,0:18:39.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Orice ce s-ar întâmpla, \Nsă nu mă atingi, bine?
Dialogue: 100,0:18:44.93,0:18:45.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bine?
Dialogue: 100,0:18:55.91,0:18:57.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Orice ce s-ar întâmpla!
Dialogue: 100,0:19:05.39,0:19:09.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}În vara următoare și în cele de după
Dialogue: 100,0:19:09.95,0:19:12.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}am continuat să vizitez pădurea.
Dialogue: 100,0:19:21.88,0:19:23.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Am plecat!
Dialogue: 100,0:19:26.31,0:19:28.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Gin! Am venit din nou și anul acesta.
Dialogue: 100,0:19:29.91,0:19:30.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Pam-pam!
Dialogue: 100,0:19:31.58,0:19:33.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Am intrat în clasa a cincea.
Dialogue: 100,0:19:36.51,0:19:37.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Cumva,
Dialogue: 100,0:19:38.08,0:19:39.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,începi să arăți din ce în \Nce mai mult ca o femeie.
Dialogue: 100,0:19:40.14,0:19:42.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ei bine, {\i1}sunt{\i0} una.
Dialogue: 100,0:19:43.49,0:19:44.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mergem?
Dialogue: 100,0:19:46.59,0:19:47.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Da.
Dialogue: 100,0:19:47.35,0:19:48.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Stai...
Dialogue: 100,0:19:48.59,0:19:49.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Asta este...
Dialogue: 100,0:19:56.34,0:19:57.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Înțeleg.
Dialogue: 100,0:19:58.20,0:19:58.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ce este?
Dialogue: 100,0:19:59.44,0:20:00.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nimic.
Dialogue: 100,0:20:01.05,0:20:02.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Chiar dacă sunt în gimnaziu acum,
Dialogue: 100,0:20:02.70,0:20:07.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,mulți dintre prietenii mei din școala primară sunt în aceeași clasă cu mine, deci nu prea s-au schimbat multe.
Dialogue: 100,0:20:08.36,0:20:10.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dar mai degrabă...
Dialogue: 100,0:20:07.82,0:20:11.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}Vârstele noastre devin mai apropiate.
Dialogue: 100,0:20:17.80,0:20:18.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Cumva,
Dialogue: 100,0:20:19.29,0:20:23.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Gin îmbătrânește mult mai încet decât oamenii.
Dialogue: 100,0:20:30.43,0:20:31.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Așa?
Dialogue: 100,0:20:32.11,0:20:35.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Da, da. Când voi începe să alerg, \Nsă-i dai drumul, bine?
Dialogue: 100,0:20:37.86,0:20:39.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Pornesc!
Dialogue: 100,0:21:13.80,0:21:19.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Odată cu trecerea timpului, \Nînfățișarea mea se schimbă,
Dialogue: 100,0:21:20.48,0:21:24.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}dar Gin arată aproape la fel ca în ziua când ne-am întâlnit prima oară.
Dialogue: 100,0:22:02.33,0:22:06.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Într-o bună zi, voi fi mai \Nbătrână ca Gin, nu-i așa?
Dialogue: 100,0:22:37.06,0:22:38.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, Hotaru.
Dialogue: 100,0:22:38.42,0:22:40.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Am tăiat un pepene. \NVino să mâncăm.
Dialogue: 100,0:22:40.60,0:22:42.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bine. Iei!
Dialogue: 100,0:22:48.59,0:22:49.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Unde este mama?
Dialogue: 100,0:22:50.17,0:22:51.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,La cumpărături cu mătușa ta.
Dialogue: 100,0:22:51.89,0:22:54.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Au mers să cumpere cadouri pentru prietenii din Yokohama.
Dialogue: 100,0:22:56.76,0:22:59.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,La ce oră vei lua trenul mâine?
Dialogue: 100,0:23:00.45,0:23:01.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nu știu,
Dialogue: 100,0:23:01.52,0:23:04.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,dar au spus că voi fi aici până în după-amiază.
Dialogue: 100,0:23:05.36,0:23:06.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Serios?
Dialogue: 100,0:23:09.18,0:23:11.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Vremea a fost bună vara asta, deci pepenii sunt foarte dulci.
Dialogue: 100,0:23:14.21,0:23:17.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dacă va continua așa, \Natunci iarna va fi una geroasă.
Dialogue: 100,0:23:18.47,0:23:19.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Serios?
Dialogue: 100,0:23:20.68,0:23:21.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Da.
Dialogue: 100,0:23:24.57,0:23:28.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Din moment ce zona asta este înconjurată de munți, iar oceanul este departe,
Dialogue: 100,0:23:28.99,0:23:31.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,diferența de temperatură \Ndintre vară și iarnă este uriașă.
Dialogue: 100,0:23:32.61,0:23:36.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Gerul iernii care vine mai \Nales după o vară toridă,
Dialogue: 100,0:23:36.38,0:23:40.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,probabil l-ar putea îngheța \Nchiar și pe zeul muntelui.
Dialogue: 100,0:23:47.44,0:23:48.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hei, unchiule...
Dialogue: 100,0:23:52.77,0:23:53.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,O eșarfă?
Dialogue: 100,0:23:54.36,0:23:55.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Da!
Dialogue: 100,0:23:55.53,0:23:57.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Te rog s-o folosești la iarnă, bine?
Dialogue: 100,0:23:59.66,0:24:00.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Pa!
Dialogue: 100,0:24:03.17,0:24:03.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bine.
Dialogue: 100,0:24:06.45,0:24:07.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ne vedem anul viitor!
Dialogue: 100,0:24:23.86,0:24:24.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Takegawa?
Dialogue: 100,0:24:25.39,0:24:27.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nu ar trebui să mergi la următoarea oră?
Dialogue: 100,0:24:28.38,0:24:30.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, ai dreptate!
Dialogue: 100,0:24:30.07,0:24:31.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Toată lumea a plecat deja.
Dialogue: 100,0:24:31.66,0:24:33.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,O voi lua înainte.
Dialogue: 100,0:24:33.21,0:24:34.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bine! Mersi.
Dialogue: 100,0:24:56.85,0:24:57.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sărut-mâna pentru masă.
Dialogue: 100,0:24:57.86,0:24:58.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ce?
Dialogue: 100,0:24:58.83,0:25:00.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ai terminat deja?
Dialogue: 100,0:25:00.42,0:25:03.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, probabil ai mâncat iar \Nînainte de cină, nu-i așa?
Dialogue: 100,0:25:03.65,0:25:05.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dacă vei continua să bagi \Ngustări, te vei îngrășa.
Dialogue: 100,0:25:05.40,0:25:07.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nu am mâncat nimic!
Dialogue: 100,0:25:07.02,0:25:08.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Doamne. Voi merge să fac o baie!
Dialogue: 100,0:25:39.35,0:25:40.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Takegawa.
Dialogue: 100,0:25:42.03,0:25:42.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ta{\alpha&HFF&}kegawa.
Dialogue: 100,0:25:42.39,0:25:42.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Take{\alpha&HFF&}gawa.
Dialogue: 100,0:25:42.64,0:25:42.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Takega{\alpha&HFF&}wa.
Dialogue: 100,0:25:42.85,0:25:43.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Takegawa.
Dialogue: 100,0:25:44.75,0:25:46.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, 'neața.
Dialogue: 100,0:25:46.79,0:25:47.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,'Neața și ție.
Dialogue: 100,0:25:47.88,0:25:50.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ai grijă pe acolo. Este înghețat.
Dialogue: 100,0:25:55.96,0:25:57.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Vei aluneca dacă nu ești atentă.
Dialogue: 100,0:26:02.12,0:26:03.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mersi.
Dialogue: 100,0:26:10.38,0:26:12.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Este frig astăzi.
Dialogue: 100,0:26:13.95,0:26:17.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ai cam fost cu capul în nori în ultimul timp, nu crezi?
Dialogue: 100,0:26:18.27,0:26:21.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,De fapt, mereu ai fost așa, dar...
Dialogue: 100,0:26:23.05,0:26:24.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Vreau...
Dialogue: 100,0:26:26.19,0:26:27.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}să-l văd pe Gin.
Dialogue: 100,0:26:52.93,0:26:53.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Vreau...
Dialogue: 100,0:26:57.17,0:26:58.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}să-l ating pe Gin.
Dialogue: 100,0:27:26.89,0:27:28.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Asta este noua ta uniformă?
Dialogue: 100,0:27:29.02,0:27:29.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Da.
Dialogue: 100,0:27:39.52,0:27:41.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Timpul chiar zboară, nu-i așa?
Dialogue: 100,0:27:41.62,0:27:43.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ai intrat deja la liceu.
Dialogue: 100,0:27:43.49,0:27:44.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Da.
Dialogue: 100,0:27:54.18,0:27:56.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nu mai vii alergând spre mine acum.
Dialogue: 100,0:27:56.61,0:28:00.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mi-am învățat lecția \Ndupă toate acele lovituri.
Dialogue: 100,0:28:08.59,0:28:09.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Abia aștept.
Dialogue: 100,0:28:10.86,0:28:15.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Peste trei ani, când voi absolvi, plănuiesc să-mi caut un serviciu aici.
Dialogue: 100,0:28:16.54,0:28:19.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Apoi voi putea să-mi \Npetrec mai mult timp cu tine.
Dialogue: 100,0:28:21.22,0:28:22.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Și toamna,
Dialogue: 100,0:28:23.11,0:28:23.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,și iarna,
Dialogue: 100,0:28:25.16,0:28:26.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,și primăvara...
Dialogue: 100,0:28:27.17,0:28:28.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tot timpul.
Dialogue: 100,0:28:29.04,0:28:29.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nu-i așa?
Dialogue: 100,0:28:35.64,0:28:36.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hotaru.
Dialogue: 100,0:28:38.04,0:28:40.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Vreau să-ți spun ceva despre mine.
Dialogue: 100,0:28:42.84,0:28:44.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nu sunt un spirit.
Dialogue: 100,0:28:45.45,0:28:46.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dar...
Dialogue: 100,0:28:47.51,0:28:48.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,nu mai sunt nici om.
Dialogue: 100,0:28:50.22,0:28:52.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Se pare că am fost cândva uman,
Dialogue: 100,0:28:52.17,0:28:53.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,dar când m-am născut,
Dialogue: 100,0:28:53.79,0:28:55.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,am fost abandonat în această pădure.
Dialogue: 100,0:28:56.90,0:29:01.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Am fost abandonat pur și simplu, \Ndeci plângeam neîncetat
Dialogue: 100,0:29:03.05,0:29:06.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,de parcă încercam să-mi chem înapoi părinții care m-au părăsit.
Dialogue: 100,0:29:08.87,0:29:10.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mi-au spus că nu m-am oprit \Ndin plâns o perioadă bună.
Dialogue: 100,0:29:17.84,0:29:21.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ar fi trebuit să mor atunci,
Dialogue: 100,0:29:22.44,0:29:26.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,dar zeul muntelui și-a făcut apariția și a pus o vrajă asupra mea care mi-a permis să-mi continui viața.
Dialogue: 100,0:29:28.00,0:29:32.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Astfel încât să nu trec în neființă.
Dialogue: 100,0:29:35.88,0:29:37.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sunt precum o fantomă.
Dialogue: 100,0:29:40.51,0:29:41.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hotaru.
Dialogue: 100,0:29:42.42,0:29:44.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Este în regulă dacă mă uiți.
Dialogue: 100,0:29:47.89,0:29:51.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Un corp care este menținut \Nprin magie este foarte firav.
Dialogue: 100,0:29:52.34,0:29:54.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dacă este atins de un om real,
Dialogue: 100,0:29:54.80,0:29:56.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,vraja se va rupe, \Niar corpul va dispărea.
Dialogue: 100,0:29:56.74,0:29:58.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Este un lucru așa de fragil.
Dialogue: 100,0:29:58.71,0:29:59.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Cât mai poți—
Dialogue: 100,0:29:59.68,0:30:01.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ceva care dispare când este atins...
Dialogue: 100,0:30:02.38,0:30:03.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Este exact ca zăpada, nu crezi?
Dialogue: 100,0:30:05.10,0:30:06.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Gin,
Dialogue: 100,0:30:07.86,0:30:11.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,eu m-am gândit la tine toată iarna.
Dialogue: 100,0:30:12.24,0:30:13.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Chiar și toamna,
Dialogue: 100,0:30:14.20,0:30:15.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,și primăvara.
Dialogue: 100,0:30:16.61,0:30:17.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Gin,
Dialogue: 100,0:30:18.21,0:30:20.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,nu mă uita.
Dialogue: 100,0:30:21.97,0:30:23.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nu mă uita.
Dialogue: 100,0:30:25.92,0:30:30.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Timpul s-ar putea să ne \Nsepare într-o bună zi.
Dialogue: 100,0:30:31.03,0:30:31.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dar,
Dialogue: 100,0:30:32.57,0:30:33.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,chiar și așa,
Dialogue: 100,0:30:34.15,0:30:35.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,până atunci,
Dialogue: 100,0:30:36.39,0:30:37.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,haide să rămânem împreună.
Dialogue: 100,0:30:42.84,0:30:44.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Festivalul spiritelor?
Dialogue: 100,0:30:44.68,0:30:47.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nu, un festival de vară ținut de spirite.
Dialogue: 100,0:30:48.08,0:30:49.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nu prea văd care e diferența.
Dialogue: 100,0:30:49.52,0:30:51.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nuanța este complet diferită!
Dialogue: 100,0:30:52.06,0:30:53.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nuanța?
Dialogue: 100,0:30:54.14,0:30:58.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Când erai mică, m-am gândit că te vei speria și de asta nu te-am invitat.
Dialogue: 100,0:30:58.79,0:31:02.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dar crezi că te-ai putea strecura afară din casă în seara asta?
Dialogue: 100,0:31:02.58,0:31:04.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Voiam să merg cu tine de mult timp.
Dialogue: 100,0:31:06.97,0:31:08.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ș-Și eu vreau!
Dialogue: 100,0:31:08.92,0:31:11.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Atunci, ne vom întâlni la \Nora opt la locul nostru.
Dialogue: 100,0:31:12.21,0:31:16.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dar un festival al spiritelor \Nsună puțin înfiorător...
Dialogue: 100,0:31:17.26,0:31:18.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Pe lângă asta, este noaptea.
Dialogue: 100,0:31:19.83,0:31:20.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nu-ți face griji.
Dialogue: 100,0:31:21.20,0:31:23.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,La suprafață nu este cu mult \Ndiferit de un festival al oamenilor.
Dialogue: 100,0:31:23.93,0:31:26.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,La urma urmei, ideea este \Nsă imite festivalurile lor.
Dialogue: 100,0:31:27.28,0:31:29.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Și te voi proteja eu, Hotaru.
Dialogue: 100,0:31:30.83,0:31:35.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Când spui lucruri de genul acesta, \Nîmi vine să sar pe tine.
Dialogue: 100,0:31:35.03,0:31:35.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fă-o.
Dialogue: 100,0:31:37.35,0:31:38.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Vorbesc serios.
Dialogue: 100,0:31:55.51,0:31:57.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stai! Așteaptă!
Dialogue: 100,0:32:17.74,0:32:21.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Chiar este exact ca un \Nfestival al oamenilor.
Dialogue: 100,0:32:21.96,0:32:23.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sunt cu toții deghizați în oameni?
Dialogue: 100,0:32:23.76,0:32:25.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Așa este. Impresionant, nu-i așa?
Dialogue: 100,0:32:25.90,0:32:29.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Am auzit că uneori chiar și oamenii le confundă fără să-și dea seama.
Dialogue: 100,0:32:31.04,0:32:32.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ca Iwa și prietenii ei, nu?
Dialogue: 100,0:32:32.89,0:32:33.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Cine?
Dialogue: 100,0:32:37.84,0:32:38.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hotaru.
Dialogue: 100,0:32:40.12,0:32:42.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Leagă-ți asta de mână.
Dialogue: 100,0:32:42.52,0:32:43.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Te vei pierde.
Dialogue: 100,0:32:48.51,0:32:50.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Parcă am fi la o întâlnire!
Dialogue: 100,0:32:51.27,0:32:53.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Este{\i0} o întâlnire.
Dialogue: 100,0:32:55.85,0:32:56.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mergem?
Dialogue: 100,0:32:57.31,0:32:57.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Da.
Dialogue: 100,0:33:25.35,0:33:26.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Poftim.
Dialogue: 100,0:33:46.24,0:33:47.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Cât de ciudat.
Dialogue: 100,0:34:00.08,0:34:01.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Vai, un cuplu!
Dialogue: 100,0:34:01.81,0:34:03.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hei!
Dialogue: 100,0:34:15.06,0:34:17.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Privește! Acel copil are o coadă!
Dialogue: 100,0:34:34.48,0:34:36.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Î-Îmi cer scuze!
Dialogue: 100,0:34:53.94,0:34:56.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uau, a fost așa de ciudat!
Dialogue: 100,0:34:56.86,0:34:59.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Cu toții s-au străduit cu \Ndeghizările lor, nu-i așa?
Dialogue: 100,0:34:59.17,0:35:01.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A fost ca un concurs de mimică!
Dialogue: 100,0:35:01.25,0:35:02.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Este așa în fiecare an?
Dialogue: 100,0:35:02.99,0:35:07.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Da, în fiecare vară...
Dialogue: 100,0:35:09.60,0:35:10.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hotaru,
Dialogue: 100,0:35:11.16,0:35:14.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,nu mai pot aștepta \Nsă vină vara viitoare.
Dialogue: 100,0:35:16.19,0:35:21.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Când nu sunt cu tine, chiar dacă știu că nu ar trebui să stau în preajma oamenilor, tot vreau să vin și să te văd.
Dialogue: 100,0:35:46.78,0:35:47.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Acea mască...
Dialogue: 100,0:35:48.61,0:35:49.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Păstreaz-o.
Dialogue: 100,0:35:56.11,0:36:02.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Probabil nu ne vom mai vedea \Nvara viitoare la locul nostru.
Dialogue: 100,0:36:05.07,0:36:08.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Asta este cu siguranță ultima oară...
Dialogue: 100,0:36:08.68,0:36:10.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Așteaptă!
Dialogue: 100,0:36:11.28,0:36:11.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ai grijă!
Dialogue: 100,0:36:14.52,0:36:15.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ești bine?
Dialogue: 100,0:36:15.83,0:36:17.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Da. Mulțumesc!
Dialogue: 100,0:36:18.29,0:36:19.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ai grijă, bine?
Dialogue: 100,0:36:29.44,0:36:30.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Gin?
Dialogue: 100,0:36:33.33,0:36:34.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Acel băiețel era un om?
Dialogue: 100,0:36:41.41,0:36:42.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Gin!
Dialogue: 100,0:36:43.12,0:36:44.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Haide, Hotaru!
Dialogue: 100,0:36:45.26,0:36:47.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,În sfârșit te pot atinge.
Dialogue: 100,0:37:28.04,0:37:29.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Te iubesc.
Dialogue: 100,0:37:29.77,0:37:30.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Da.
Dialogue: 100,0:37:31.64,0:37:32.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Și eu te iubesc.
Dialogue: 100,0:37:55.40,0:37:56.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Verde închis.
Dialogue: 100,0:37:57.90,0:37:59.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Asta este pădurea zeului muntelui.
Dialogue: 100,0:38:04.14,0:38:06.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hotaru. Îți mulțumim.
Dialogue: 100,0:38:07.21,0:38:11.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Noi voiam ca Gin să fie pe vecie cu noi, dar...
Dialogue: 100,0:38:11.07,0:38:16.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Gin voia să atingă un om.
Dialogue: 100,0:38:16.73,0:38:20.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,În sfârșit a fost îmbrățișat de un om.
Dialogue: 100,0:38:21.57,0:38:23.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Probabil nu voi mai putea...
Dialogue: 100,0:38:26.24,0:38:28.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}să aștept cu nerăbdare vara pentru mult timp.
Dialogue: 100,0:38:29.68,0:38:30.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sufletul o să mă doară.
Dialogue: 100,0:38:31.74,0:38:33.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Lacrimile îmi vor curge.
Dialogue: 100,0:38:34.48,0:38:42.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dar căldura ce o simt în mâinile mele și amintirile din această vară vor rămâne pe vecie în inima mea.
Dialogue: 100,0:38:50.65,0:38:52.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Deci, haide.
Dialogue: 100,0:38:57.33,0:38:58.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Să mergem.
