Dialogue: 1,0:42:56.65,0:43:03.09,ED TL,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.8\fad(150,300)}Nu voi uita niciodată
Dialogue: 1,0:43:04.37,0:43:10.57,ED TL,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.8\fad(150,300)}aceste zile aurii de vară
Dialogue: 1,0:43:11.24,0:43:18.12,ED TL,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.8\fad(150,300)}Acea vară care mi-a adus fericire
Dialogue: 1,0:43:19.41,0:43:25.70,ED TL,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.8\fad(150,300)}în viața mea plictisitoare
Dialogue: 1,0:43:31.39,0:43:44.49,ED TL,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.8\fad(150,300)}Privește acum, vara a revenit
Dialogue: 1,0:43:45.31,0:43:57.60,ED TL,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.8\fad(150,300)}ca să mă ajute să-mi țin promisiunea pe care am făcut atunci
